of Sofia's Technical University and hospitals to which he will
grant donations.
</P>
<P>
Kinkel and Prime Minister Kostov, along with businessmen, will
take part in a Bulgarian-German economic seminar on the promotion
of trade relations between the two countries.
</P>
<P>
A group of German parliamentarians, diplomats, businessmen and
journalists will be on the delegation list led by Kinkel.
</P>
<P>
This will be Kinkel's second visit to Bulgaria this year,
following his visit to Plovdiv on March 27. 
