<HEADLINE> Cypriot Government Pledges All-out Support to </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NICOSIA, October 8 (Xinhua) -- The Cypriot government has
pledged that it will take every possible measure to develop the
agricultural sector, which constitutes an important part of the
economy.
</P>
<P>
The pledge was made by Minister of Agriculture, Natural
Resources and Environment Costas Petrides at the opening ceremony
of the 10th Agri-Fair, the Water Technology Exhibition and the
Machine and Tools Exhibition.
</P>
