additional 47 million Cyprus pounds (about 90 million
U.S. dollars) to the agricultural sector besides the annual
budget provisions for agriculture.
</P>
<P>
The minister made special reference to the problems created by
adverse weather conditions in the past few years, the
unprecedented and prolonged drought, saying that the water
technology exhibition is aimed at projecting new technology
related to the provision, management and use of water.
</P>
