calling on the military junta "to take immediate steps to restore
democracy in Sierra Leone."
</P>
<P>
The sanctions, however, will hurt the "poor Sierra Leonean
civilians," said Aliu Kamara, spokesman of Sierra Leone's current
supreme Armed Forced Revolutionary Council (AFRC), Wednesday.
(Sierra Leone-Sanctions)
</P>
<P>
