<HEADLINE> Weather Forecast for Major World Cities </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, October 9 (Xinhua) -- Weather forecast for 11 major
world cities from 20:00 today to 20:00 on October 10, issued by
China's Central Meteorological Station tonight:
</P>
<P>
Beijing: min. 11 degrees C., max. 24 degrees C., clear, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Tokyo: min. 15 degrees C., max. 23 degrees C., drizzle, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Bangkok: min. 27 degrees C., max. 35 degrees C., cloudy, calm
to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Sydney: min. 12 degrees C., max. 21 degrees C., clear, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Karachi: min. 25 degrees C., max. 36 degrees C., clear, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Cairo: min. 18 degrees C., max. 29 degrees C., clear, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Moscow: min. 1 degree C., max. 7 degrees C., overcast to
drizzle, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Frankfurt: min. 15 degrees C., max. 20 degrees C., drizzle,
calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Paris: min. 15 degrees C., max. 19 degrees C., drizzle, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
London: min. 14 degrees C., max. 18 degrees C., moderate rain
to drizzle, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
New York: min. 16 degrees C., max. 23 degrees C., drizzle, calm
to gentle breeze. 
</P>
