treaty initialed by the two sides Wednesday as an extremely
important step in the relations between the two countries.
</P>
<P>
"It will make Mexico an even more attractive investment
location for small- and medium-sized German enterprises," he added.
</P>
<P>
Both leaders also expressed satisfaction with the signing of a
framework agreement on technical cooperation on Wednesday and said
that they wanted to expand relations.
</P>
<P>
Zedillo, who started a five-day official visit to Germany on
Tuesday, has met German President Roman Herzog and Chancellor
Helmut Kohl over the past two days. He is also due to visit
several German cities. 
