country attaches great importance to its ties with China.
</P>
<P>
Kucan made the remark when meeting with Chinese Vice Foreign
Minister Zhang Deguang in this capital.
</P>
<P>
There should be more and better cooperation between the two
countries in both politics and economy, he said.
(Slovenia-China-Ties) 
