<TEXT>
<P>
MADRID, October 8 (Xinhua) -- Jeannie Longo-Ciprelli of France
took her 12th World Cycling Championship title, and retained her
time trial gold for the third consecutive year in San Sebastian,
Spain, on Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
Longo, who had won the event at Duitama, Colombia, and Lugano,
Switzerland, completed the 28-kilometer course in 39 minutes and
