from all over the world and about 70 journalists from Latin
America, organizers said.
</P>
<P>
The fair, which was first held in 1994, aims to showcase
Panama's tourist resources and to attract new clients in Latin
America, Europe and the United States, said Pinki Van Der Hans,
president of the organizing committee.
</P>
<P>
