and connecting the two American continents, has both modern
buildings like those in the metropolises of the hemisphere and
beautiful landscapes rich in environmental diversity, he said.
</P>
<P>
Officials of the Panamanian Institute of tourism said Panama
will host more than 470,000 foreign visitors in 1997, expected to
generate 460 million U.S. dollars. 
