kind to be exported.
</P>
<P>
The crane was manufactured by China's Lanzhou Locomotive
Plant. It is learnt that the manufacturer beat out four contenders
from the US and Britain when it won the bid for a crane for the
Railways Ministry of Pakistan in May 1996.
</P>
